The White House has sent several nominations to the Senate for approval. These include Debo P. Adegbile to be an Assistant Attorney General, Marc A. Kastner to be Director of the Office of Science at the Department of Energy, Harry James Franklyn Korrell III to be a Member of the Board of Directors of the Legal Services Corporation, Mark E. Lopes to be a Member of the Board of Directors of the Inter-American Foundation, Victor B. Maddox to be a Member of the Board of Directors of the Legal Services Corporation, Vivek Hallegere Murthy to be Medical Director and Surgeon General of the Public Health Service, and Franklin M. Orr, Jr. to be Under Secretary for Science at the Department of Energy.